an'; font-size:12pt">ing</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> through sustainable development activities for inclusion of persons with disability in the job markets and providing equalizations are the followings:</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:Wingdings; font-size:12pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Needs assessments </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">survey </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">for persons with disability with </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">data </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">collection </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">with</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> interest</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> of P.W.D for interest</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">able</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> vocational training</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> for </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">sustainable jobs</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">  </span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:Wingdings; font-size:12pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Lobby and</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> advocacy for implementation</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> the Afghan law in general public</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:Wingdings; font-size:12pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Providing sustainable rehabilitations services with durable Artificial limbs and Outhouse’s</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:Wingdings; font-size:12pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Micro-Credit for self/help socio economical business.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:Wingdings; font-size:12pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Assistive technology such as wheelchairs, White Can and Crutches</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> </span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:Wingdings; font-size:12pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Improvement of the physical accessibility with Ramps constructions and adaptation of classes and doo</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">r</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> steps</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> schools</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">DFID </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">activities </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">in Afghanistan</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">:</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">As far as I know DFID</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> in Afghanistan,</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> they are spending</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> for supporting the government,</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> and</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> also providing</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">huge support</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> to </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">International Organization as implementing partners for developmental and humanitarian’s</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> affair</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">. For Afghan disabled people NGOs,</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">they have very limited support to persons with disability in Afghanistan.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> I several time knocked the door of DFID in Afghanistan</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">,</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> they</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> only</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> said that we are supporting the International Organizations not have so far plan to support local NGOs. </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">There are very limited NGOs running by persons with disability </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">working </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">for </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">the </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">mission and vision to support persons with disability</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> in Afghanistan</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">. I</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">n the present context</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">, many of the Afghan disabled people organization are collapsed</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> due to the 2014</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> alarm of the media. </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">The Afghan government has no systems to support the </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Afghan </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">CSOs, DPOs and NGOs</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">. Several Afghan NGOs working for persons with disability has </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">shortage of</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> funding for </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">their </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">activities and administrative support </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">because;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> the </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">donor’s</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> agencies are not interesting to support disability development activities</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> in Afghanistan because, it is not related to politics</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">DFID must take the responsibility to capacit</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">at</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">e the Afghan NGOs for expandable support to persons with </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">disability</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> in the following systems:</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:Wingdings; font-size:12pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Mainstreaming disability as top agenda</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:Wingdings; font-size:12pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Providing long term developmental project with sustainable mission and vision</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-indent